data.description: Short Sale. This is a SHORT SALE.  This sale is contingent upon lenders approval of short sale offer. Short sale approval of seller's lender may be conditioned upon the gross commission being reduced. Short sale could take up to 3 months for approval.  Experience the epitome of Florida living in this charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in the desirable Silverado community. Boasting a meticulously maintained front lawn and an inviting open-concept layout, this home exudes warmth and comfort from the moment you arrive. Entertain with ease in the spacious living, dining, and kitchen areas flooded with natural light, while the well-appointed kitchen features modern appliances, ample cabinet space, a large granite counter, and a convenient center island and breakfast bar. Plus, with recent updates including new tiles in the living and dining area in 2022 and updated appliances purchased in 2019, modern living is at its finest.  Retreat to the expansive master bedroom complete with a private bath featuring dual sinks, a wide counter, and a walk-in closet, offering a peaceful sanctuary to relax and rejuvenate. The remaining bedrooms are thoughtfully designed with ceiling fans, built-in closets, and plush carpeting for added comfort. A dedicated laundry room with cabinets and shelves adds to the home's functionality, while the attached 2-car garage and concrete driveway provide ample parking and storage space. Step outside to discover your own private paradise, with a fully tiled lanai and a sprawling fenced-in backyard, providing the perfect backdrop for outdoor gatherings or simply enjoying the serene surroundings. Conveniently located to the community pool, playground, clubhouse, and scenic trails, as well as nearby recreational amenities like the Tennis Center and Zephyr Water Park, there's no shortage of activities to enjoy. Ideally located just minutes from shopping, dining, entertainment, and major roadways, including Gall Blvd, Wiregrass, and Premium Outlets, this home offers the perfect combination of tranquility and convenience. Don't miss out on this opportunity to live your best life in Silverado!
